    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.37-38_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">37</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <salute>Dear Mr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>We were shocked and saddened when we heard today, after a few days out of the city, of the passing of Mrs. Neihardt.</p>
                
                <p>There is so little folks can say or do to help at such
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.37-38_0002"/>
                
                    <note type="curatorial"><hi rend="caps">JOHN G. NEIHARDT CENTER</hi></note>
                
                    times, but we do want you to know we are thinking of you and your family.  We know how much you will all miss her.  In fact, all who knew her will miss her, as she was a wonderful person.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Our love to you and your family,</salute>
                
                    <signed>Ward and Marie Moore.</signed>
                
                    <address>
                        <addrLine><unclear>St.</unclear> Louis, Mo.</addrLine>
                        <addrLine><unclear>April</unclear> 20, 1958.</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
            
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.37-38_0003"/>
                
                <ab type="return">
                    Moore
                    6015 Aresenal St.
                    St. Louis 9, Mo
                </ab>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    SAINT LOUIS, MO. 3
                    APR21
                    230 PM
                    1958
                
                    PRAY
                    FOR
                    PEACE
                </ab>
                <figure>
                    <figDesc>3 Cent Stamp</figDesc>
                    <p>U.S. POSTAGE 3Â¢
                    IN GOD WE TRUST
                    LIBERTY</p>
                </figure>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">38</fw>
                
                <ab type="address">
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Mr. John Neihardt</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Route #7</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Columbia</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Missouri.</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </ab>
                
            </div1>
